Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:37.20,Autor,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,200)}Překlad:   Špendla
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:37.20,Autor,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(146,245)}Korektura:   Phibo
